-text"><cite class="citation web">Gelevan, Douglas (2 April 2010). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://dgelevan.wordpress.com/2010/04/02/getting-ripped-brett-gaylors-rip-a-remix-manifesto-a-case-study/">"Getting \'RiP\'ped \xe2\x80\x93 Brett Gaylor\'s RiP: A Remix Manifesto"</a>. <i>Douglas Gelevan Reports</i><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">2014-05-19</span></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARiP%21%3A+A+Remix+Manifesto&amp;rft.atitle=Getting+%27RiP%27ped+%E2%80%93+Brett+Gaylor%27s+RiP%3A+A+Remix+Manifesto&amp;rft.aufirst=Douglas&amp;rft.aulast=Gelevan&amp;rft.date=2010-04-02&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Douglas+Gelevan+Reports&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fdgelevan.wordpress.com%2F2010%2F04%2F02%2Fgetting-ripped-brett-gaylors-rip-a-remix-manifesto-a-case-study%2F&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>\n<li id="cite_note-8"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-8">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://wiki.creativecommons.org/wiki/Case_Studies/RIP:_A_Remix_Manifesto">IP:_A_Remix_Manifesto</a> on creativecommons.org</span></li>\n<li id="cite_note-9"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-9">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation news"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.canada.com/montrealgazette/news/arts/story.html?id=e88e2492-f6cb-4059-ba2a-17e79ed736b7">"RiP: A Remix Manifesto: review"</a>. <i>Canada.com</i>. 16 October 2008<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">2014-05-19</span></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARiP%21%3A+A+Remix+Manifesto&amp;rft.atitle=RiP%3A+A+Remix+Manifesto%3A+review&amp;rft.date=2008-10-16&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.